data.description:
PRICE REDUCTION! And $10,000 towards BUYER'S CLOSING COSTS or buy down from seller! At this list price PLUS the closing cost assistance, - WOW!! 
Better than NEW - fully landscaped front & back yards, quiet street & meticulously maintained!  Upgraded, beautiful, 2688 sq. ft ,4 bedroom, 2.5 bath plus loft home. It has granite countertops, 42'' dark brown upgraded cabinetry in the kitchen, & bathrooms, stainless steel appliances, including a gas stove, kitchen roi system & a soft water system that services the entire home! Tandem FOUR car garage - unheard of, right? Perfect for those LARGE EXTENDED CAB TRUCKS!!!  Work from home? No problem - this roomy home has an additional loft and several living spaces. Easy care wood-look tile on the first floor & carpeting upstair The backyard landscaping includes pavers, easy-care artificial grass, the fruit trees - lemon, orange & grapefruit and a covered patio with mountain views. Buckeye is growing with it's brand new Costco and additional shops and restaurants downtown Buckeye as well as in Verrado.
